{"tid":2237223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"被釘牌教師親筆感言謝鼓勵：留言打氣是守護香港教育界最重要支柱","createTime":"2020-10-10T05:41:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T07:43:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"1eda8b3fda52bc6f5b9b1dad9e95f41e0874a532","tid":2237223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:41:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/haGlGmVI22iRHmPeczfHmTyozwo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XARROTUUBVGUBBKHY5GCQQD3UE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhaGlGmVI22iRHmPeczfHmTyozwo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXARROTUUBVGUBBKHY5GCQQD3UE.jpg&h=67f30d8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九龍塘宣道小學一名教師被指有計劃地散播「港獨」信息，被教育局以「嚴重專業失德」為由取消註冊，並終身不能踏足校園。事件引起軒然大波，今日（10日）教協將該名小學教師的親筆信上載Facebook專頁，信中感謝市民的關心及支持，並指市民的留言及打氣都是守護香港教育界最重要的支柱，勉勵大家加油。<br />\n<br />\n教協今日上載該名小學教師的親筆信到Facebook專頁，信中該教師提到，市民的留言及打氣都是守護香港教育界最重要的支柱，並在信末寫上「大家加油」，教協的帖子中加上「StandwithTeachers」的標籤。教協稱，自事件發生以來，建制陣營不斷誣蔑老師與中傷教育界，教協深感痛心，但幸有港人打氣及支持，與教育界並肩同行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/YRMTVSGFXZH5FES6CGLVRY5BEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FYRMTVSGFXZH5FES6CGLVRY5BEU%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDPcTfOzAwtSP2zPdisjLlXU%3D&h=fa19cfe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FYRMTVSGFXZH5FES6CGLVRY5BEU%2F&h=458e6c65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/YRMTVSGFXZH5FES6CGLVRY5BEU/</a>"},{"pid":"0fa97c1a6cba1954edd5e0352d01640ffae347ac","tid":2237223,"uid":66527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:42:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cr